Company Overview of Deroy & Devereaux Private Investment Counsel, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Deroy & Devereaux Private Investment Counsel, Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. It also manages caters to pension and profit sharing plans, Taft Hartley pension plans, municipal pension plans, foundations, endowments, and professional corporations, and state or municipal government entities. The firm manages separate client-focused equity portfolios. It invests in the public equity markets of the United States. Deroy & Devereaux Private Investment Counsel, Inc. was founded in 2002 and is based in Southfield, Michigan.


