Experience

D&D is staffed with seven portfolio managers who share a common value approach to investing. Our team is deep in experience with nearly 200 years combined investment experience at work for our clients.MORE


Philosophy

DeRoy & Devereaux is a fundamental valuation based asset management firm.  Our value investment philosophy is rooted in the belief that competitive investment returns come principally through researching companies that we have identified as attractive investment candidates and acquiring them at reasonable prices.MORE


Investment

The firm is designed to limit distractions and bureaucracy allowing investment professionals to focus on generating investment results for our clients.INSTITUTIONALHIGH NET WORTH

 













